# .env.example — V12 Universal OR Strategy
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values.
# NEVER commit .env — it is gitignored.
# All secrets used in CI/CD are stored as GitHub Actions Secrets (Settings > Secrets).

# ── GitHub Actions Secrets (CI/CD) ───────────────────────────────────────────
# GITHUB_TOKEN         Auto-provided by GitHub Actions. Do not set manually.
# SONAR_TOKEN          SonarCloud project token. Set in GitHub Actions Secrets.
# GCP_CREDENTIALS      Google Cloud service account JSON key (base64). CI only.
# DEEPSEEK_API_KEY     DeepSource integration token. CI only.

# ── Local Development Overrides ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# These keys are read by scripts/ utilities, NOT by the NinjaTrader strategy.
# The strategy itself uses NinjaTrader Properties panel for all configuration.

# Optional: Path override for the droid CLI binary (default: %USERPROFILE%\bin\droid)
# DROID_BIN_PATH=C:\Users\YourName\bin\droid

# Optional: NinjaTrader documents root path override
# Used by deploy-sync.ps1 if the default path differs from the standard install.
# NT_DOCUMENTS_PATH=C:\Users\YourName\Documents\NinjaTrader 8

# Optional: IPC server port for the Control Surface app
# Default is 5001. Change if port conflict with another NT instance.
# V12_IPC_PORT=5001

# ── Observability (Local) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# SENTRY_DSN           Sentry Data Source Name (future Phase 5 integration)
# LANGSMITH_API_KEY    LangSmith tracing key for multi-agent reasoning chains
